headline: Looking At The Narrative For IREN After AI Cloud Deals And Split Analyst Views
summary: The latest update to the IREN story centers on a slightly higher fair value estimate, now set at US$83.00 versus the prior US$81.85, along with a small reduction in the discount rate from 8.18% to 8.11% as analysts recalibrate how they weigh future cash flows.
